attributionInfo.brokerName: Leading Edge Realty Group, Inc. RE/MAX Leading Edge

data.description:
Welcome to this charming single-family home in the serene Azalea Estates. Fantastic Cabarrus County schools.
The floorpan is well thought! 2-story, 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath, Bonus room and a Study, making it a highly functional property. The open floor plan creates a spacious feel, complemented by an attached two-car garage. Step onto the open porch or relax on the covered patio.
Upon entering, you have a dedicated study/office and a formal dining area and a bright, spacious great room. It flows into sunny breakfast nook and a large open kitchen.
The kitchen boasts modern stainless steel appliances and a large granite center island.
Upstairs, discover the spacious bedrooms, laundry room and a versatile bonus room. 
Huge backyard topography is a plus! When you go up the stairs you get a large area and imagine building a fire-pit, a gazebo or any outdoor living space! It has huge potential!
